  "Patrick Collison is the cofounder and CEO of Stripe, a company that lets businesses and individuals accept payments over the internet.",
  "In September 2018, Stripe announced a $245 million funding round that valued the business at $20.25 billion.",
  "He and his brother John hatched the idea for Stripe while both were in college in Boston at MIT.",
  "Stripe's first payment was processed while the Collison brothers were on vacation in South America.",
